snippet.title: Winds of Change - Announcement Trailer (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
🦊 Experience the Ultimate Furry Tale! 🐺

Winds of Change - a powerful visual novel about shaping the world with your choices is coming to Nintendo Switch on June 3rd!

- Developer: Klace - twitter.com/klace
- Publisher: Crunching Koalas - crunchingkoalas.com
